 Mr. Japanese Women's Coach.

258
00:17:08,600 --> 00:17:11,190
Oh, why thank you!

259
00:17:11,190 --> 00:17:15,550
But doing two weight classes in one day would be too much, even for Yawara-san.


260
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:19,510
Just think it over.

261
00:17:19,510 --> 00:17:23,230
You have until the day before the free-weights to choose your player.

262
00:17:23,230 --> 00:17:24,230
Right.


263
00:17:25,040 --> 00:17:29,020
