272
00:17:58,470 --> 00:18:02,400
That's amazing, Inokuma-san! You're really in your groove!

273
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:04,000
Did it hurt, Fujiko-san?

274
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,100
Nope.

275
00:18:12,800 --> 00:18:16,820
